In March 2020, its US and foreign money market funds faced redemption reque=
sts. The US funds raised money from MMLF as intended, but the foreign fund =
couldn=E2=80=99t. JPMorgan sensibly thought =E2=80=9Cwell these are money m=
arket funds, it=E2=80=99s all short-term low-risk stuff, surely there is a =
