l them to the Fed.=E2=80=9D JPMorgan=E2=80=99s US funds are=C2=A0in the bus=
iness of investing in short-term cash-equivalent securities, and being in t=
he middle of this trade is in fact a low-risk short-term cash-equivalent=C2=
=A0sort of trade. The foreign fund goes to the US fund and says =E2=80=9Cwe=
=E2=80=99ll pay you a 1.3% annualized yield to hold this stuff for us overn=
ight and then hand it to the Fed in the morning,=E2=80=9D and the US fund i=
