ny guidance that would prevent the hypothetical transaction.</p></blockquot=
e><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So JPMorgan did this to the tune of $4.3 bil=
lion of assets.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But last week the SEC objec=
